OL,6,FA girl held in a young offenders'
OL,7,Finstitution was pinned down and
OL,8,Fforcibly stripped by a group of male
OL,9,Fprison guards, according to a watchdog.
OL,11,FChief Inspector of Prisons Charlie
OL,12,FTaylor said he was "deeply shocked" at
OL,13,Fthe findings, which revealed the
OL,14,F"incredibly vulnerable" teenage
OL,15,Fprisoner had been restrained and had
OL,16,Fher clothes removed by "multiple men"
OL,17,Fon two occasions at YOI Wetherby in
OL,18,FWest Yorkshire.
