OL,6,FHolding some of the most "challenging"
OL,7,Fchildren in the country, the watchdog
OL,8,Flikened the "complex group" of
OL,9,Fyoungsters behind bars there to the
OL,10,Fequivalent of being as dangerous as
OL,11,Fmen in category A adult jails.
OL,13,FNearly half of the children at
OL,14,FWetherby have previously been in
OL,15,Fcouncil care and the site has the
OL,16,F"highest rate of self-harm of any
OL,17,Fprison in the country", with officers
OL,18,Foften having to intervene "multiple
OL,19,Ftimes at night" to stop girls trying
OL,20,Fto harm themselves, inspectors said.
