OL,6,FDuring the inspection, carried out in
OL,7,FNovember and December last year, wider
OL,8,Fconcerns about how often child inmates
OL,9,Fwere being strip-searched while being
OL,10,Frestrained and the use of force
OL,11,Fagainst them were also raised.
OL,13,FSome 24 children were strip-searched
OL,14,Fin the last 12 months, with 12 of
OL,15,Fthose taking place while they were
OL,16,Fbeing restrained.
