OL,6,FAlthough prison bosses had recorded
OL,7,Fthe decision to carry out a strip-
OL,8,Fsearch, "none had recorded the
OL,9,Fauthority to use restraint", according
OL,10,Fto the findings.
OL,12,FTechniques that deliberately cause
OL,13,Fpain in a bid to restrain a child had
OL,14,Fbeen used nine times in the last 12
OL,15,Fmonths but were deemed "inappropriate"
OL,16,Fon each occasion by an independent
OL,17,Freview panel.
